document_data.History:
In the [[Arena of Blood]] in [[Manshaka]], hungry otyughs were kept to devour the carcasses of the slain, but they would seize an unlucky contestant given the chance. In the {{YearlinkName|1357}}, [[Vajra Valmeyjar]] drove a [[troll]] into its tentacles.{{Cite comic/Cat & Mouse|10, 12}}

In [[1357 DR]], otyughs could occasionally be found in the [[sewers of Waterdeep]].

Between [[1488 DR]] and [[1492 DR]], an unknown number of otyughs inhabited the bottom of the [[Refuse pit (Port Nyanzaru)|Refuse pit]] in [[Port Nyanzaru]] and ate their fill daily. Thanks to their presence, the pit would not reach its brim.<ref>
